WEBVTT

00:00:57.773 --> 00:01:00.137
And then he posed a question

00:01:00.161 --> 00:01:03.007
that I couldn't get out of my head:

00:01:04.095 --> 00:01:10.036
"Katherine, what is wrong with the drugs?"

00:01:13.090 --> 00:01:18.022
I spent the next 10 years
trying to track down the answer.

00:01:18.621 --> 00:01:21.439
Our health care system relies on generics.

00:01:21.463 --> 00:01:23.371
My family does, too.

00:01:24.387 --> 00:01:26.144
But a decade of interviews,

00:01:26.168 --> 00:01:28.255
meetings with whistleblowers,

00:01:28.279 --> 00:01:32.045
on-the-ground reporting
across four continents